name: static-info
vimscript:
let SessionLoad = 1
let s:so_save = &g:so | let s:siso_save = &g:siso | setg so=0 siso=0 | setl so=-1 siso=-1
let v:this_session=expand("<sfile>:p")
silent only
silent tabonly
cd ~/code/github/dotfiles
if expand('%') == '' && !&modified && line('$') <= 1 && getline(1) == ''
  let s:wipebuf = bufnr('%')
endif
let s:shortmess_save = &shortmess
if &shortmess =~ 'A'
  set shortmess=aoOA
else
  set shortmess=aoO
endif
badd +303 ~/code/github/dotfiles/.config/nvim/lua/experiments/static-info.lua
argglobal
%argdel
tabnew +setlocal\ bufhidden=wipe
tabrewind
edit ~/code/github/dotfiles/.config/nvim/lua/experiments/static-info.lua
argglobal
let s:cpo_save=&cpo
set cpo&vim

nnoremap <buffer> <silent> gr :lua require'nvim-treesitter-refactor.smart_rename'.smart_rename(1520)
